snippet.title: Assault Cube - gameplay HD
snippet.description:
Free-to-play MMOFPS with fast action and realistic environments.

Multi-platform (for Mac, Windows and Linux) open source shooter game using the CUBE engine and with very minimal requirements.

You can play Assault Cube on a Laptop through a broadband internet connection.

Official Site: http://assault.cubers.net/
